Document Control
Responsibilities
Coordinate all activities related to the document control procedures, including technical documents, drawing and commercial correspodence;Input document data into the standard registers ensuring that the information is accurate and up to date;Generate the various document control reports as required. Requirements:Candidate must possess at least a Diploma, Bachelor's Degree, any field.Required skill(s): Ability to keep clear and accurate records and reports, good communication, knowledge in use of spreadsheets database and selected job specific software, ability to use computer and rapidly input data and retrieve records.Required language(s): English (minimum passive) , Bahasa IndonesiaAt least 1 year(s) of working experience as document control is advantageFresh graduate are welcomePreferably Staff (non-management & non-supervisor)s specializing in Administration & Documentation or equivalent.Full-Time position(s) available.
